media$description.$t:
Schools for the deaf (K-12) block YouTube & Vimeo for various reasons and they often have to ask their tech specialist(s) for permission to open up ASLized's channel for the day if they're lucky. 

Instead of doing this every time a teacher needs to show videos, ASLized wants to mail DVDs and is seeking sponsors to cover the cumulative cost of printing/recording/shipping.

Contact ASLized at contact@aslized.org if you wish to help!

Contact ASLized at contact@aslized.org if you wish to help!
